          <li>Kaomoji</li>
          <li>Decorative symbols and special characters</li>
          <li>Platform usage guides and tips</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 style={{
          fontSize: '1.5rem',
          fontWeight: '600',
          marginBottom: '1rem',
          color: 'var(--accent-color)'
        }}>
          2. User Responsibilities
