          fontWeight: '600',
          marginBottom: '1rem',
          color: 'var(--accent-color)'
        }}>
          8. Terms Modifications
        </h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new terms on this website. Continued use of the service constitutes acceptance of the modified terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 style={{
          fontSize: '1.5rem',
          fontWeight: '600',
          marginBottom: '1rem',
          color: 'var(--accent-color)'
        }}>
          9. Governing Law
        </h2>
        <p>
          These terms are governed by and construed in accordance with local laws. Any legal actions shall be brought in the courts of the jurisdiction where the website operates.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section style={{
        marginTop: '2rem',
        padding: '1.5rem',
        background: 'var(--bg-color)',
        borderRadius: 'var(--radius-lg)',
        borderLeft: '4px solid var(--accent-color)'
      }}>
        <h2 style={{
          fontSize: '1.25rem',
          fontWeight: '600',
          marginBottom: '1rem',
          color: 'var(--accent-color)'
        }}>
          ðŸ“§ Contact Us
        </h2>
        <p style={{ marginBottom: '0.5rem' }}>
          For any questions, please contact:
        </p>
        <p style={{ fontWeight: '600', color: 'var(--accent-color)' }}>
